text: Margaret Lake is located in Kittitas County, Washington. The lake is a popular area for hiking.http://www.wta.org/go-hiking/hikes/margaret-lake/ Margaret Lake] at Washington Trails Association. It's also stocked with rainbow trout.Fish Stocking for Margaret Lake at Washington Department of Fish and Wildlife site. ==References== ==External links== *GNIS Feature Detail Report for Margaret Lake Category:Lakes of Washington (state) Category:Lakes of Kittitas County, Washington
